    "_postman_id": "cms-doctors-api-collection",
    "name": "CMS - Doctor Management API",
    "description": "Doctor Management API collection for the Clinic Management System with Clean Architecture.\n\n## üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è Doctor Management API (/api/doctors)\n\nThis collection focuses specifically on doctor management endpoints:\n\n- **Doctor Profile CRUD**: Create, read, update, and delete doctor profiles\n- **User-Doctor Relationship**: Manage associations between users and doctor profiles\n- **Medical Specializations**: Track and manage doctor specializations\n- **License Management**: Medical license validation and tracking\n- **Experience Tracking**: Years of experience and professional background\n- **Contact Information**: Philippine and US phone number validation\n- **Professional Details**: Medical degree, certifications, and qualifications\n\n## Testing Coverage\n\n- ‚úÖ Doctor profile creation with all required fields\n- ‚úÖ Doctor retrieval (single and list)\n- ‚úÖ Doctor profile updates and modifications\n- ‚úÖ Doctor profile deletion\n- ‚úÖ User-Doctor relationship management\n- ‚úÖ Specialization validation\n- ‚úÖ License number validation\n- ‚úÖ Phone number validation (PH/US formats)\n- ‚úÖ Error handling (validation, not found, duplicates)\n- ‚úÖ Professional details management\n\n## Environment Variables\n\nThis collection uses the following environment variables:\n- `cms_local`: http://localhost:4000 (for local development)\n- `cms_prod`: https://capstone-api.up.railway.app (for production)\n- `baseUrl`: Base URL for API endpoints\n- `authToken`: JWT token for authenticated requests\n- Various test data variables for dynamic testing",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": {
      "major": 2,
      "minor": 3,
      "patch": 0
    }
  },
